step 1 : open cmd as administator 
    how open : 1 . win+s 
               2. select cmd and click right and select open as administator 

step 2 : enter this command :- 
         1.  this command is lock your folder 

            icacls "D:\demofolder" /deny Everyone:(OI)(CI)F

         note :- hare demofolder is name of folder to write any folder name hare 
               
         2.  unlock folder command :- 

            takeown /f "D:\demofolder" /r /d y

          note :- hare demofolder is name of folder to write same folder name that you unlock your folder
      
